import React from 'react'; import '../App.css'; {/* About page */} function About() { return (

Since 2019, we have been providing users and customers the best experience.

At ToUpper LLC, we pride and distinguish ourselves by using the most modern

technology and approach when creating applications for our clients. We help

our clients to ensure that their business succeeds and meets their goals by

providing the most elegant and easy to use application for their customers.

During our process, we organize our requirements and make sure that your application

is met within a timely manner. In order to ensure that your application is the best out

there, we test our applications to assure for security, bugs, and any other issues that

may come your way. We will also publish your application for you for the world to see

and provide any maintenance that your application may need. For any S.E.O, surveys,

or marketing needs, we will be happy to discuss on the best marketing approach for

your application!

Let the geeks help! We know creating a website isn't easy, so let us do

the hard work for you. Please contact us and provide any questions

or comments you may have! We will be happy to provide a free first

consultation.



For any concerns with our applications that are available on the

Google Play or Apple App store, please contact us and we'll be happy to address whatever it is you need.

); } export default About;
